Package: orbitr
Type: Package
Title: A Tidy Physics Engine for Building and Visualizing Orbital Simulations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Dave", "Rosenman",
      email = "dave.rosenman.data@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A lightweight, fully vectorized N-body physics engine built for
    the R ecosystem. Simulate and visualize complex orbital mechanics,
    celestial trajectories, and gravitational interactions using modern
    tidyverse principles. Features multiple numerical integration methods,
    including the energy-conserving Velocity Verlet algorithm, to ensure
    highly stable orbital propagation.
URL: https://drosenman.github.io/orbitr/, https://github.com/DRosenman/orbitr
BugReports: https://github.com/DRosenman/orbitr/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
